content:
PR CI fails with 503 download error soon after starting.

https://www.githubstatus.com/incidents/cypv026dr23w
I'm going to guess #92804 is having the same problem
That one's slightly different but similar, so probably the same
I can try force pushing my PR to see if restarting CI fixes it
It didn't, as far as I can tell the PR isn't malformed (maybe I'm missing something though?) so probably it's related
It's definitely not your PR; if it's anything other than this incident, it'd be a random failure, but I'm pretty sure it's the incident
We'll just have to wait out the incident
